OL,3,CPensioner households affected by cuts
OL,4,Cto winter fuel support to receive #100
OL,6,FAll pensioner households affected by
OL,7,Fcuts to winter fuel support are to
OL,8,Freceive a one-off payment of #100.
OL,10,FEarlier this year, the Labour
OL,11,FGovernment announced that winter fuel
OL,12,Fpayments would be means-tested.
OL,14,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons told
OL,15,Fthe Northern Ireland Assembly he had
OL,16,Fbid for and received #17million to
OL,17,Fmitigate against the changes.
