OL,3,CPensioner households affected by cuts
OL,4,Cto winter fuel support to receive #100
OL,6,FHe told MLAs: "I can confirm a one-off
OL,7,Fwinter fuel payment of #100 will be
OL,8,Fpaid to all pensioner households
OL,9,Faffected by the Labour Government's
OL,10,Fdecision."
OL,12,FMr Lyons added: "This payment will be
OL,13,Fmade available to all pensioner
OL,14,Fhouseholds who have had their winter
OL,15,Ffuel payments removed.
OL,17,F"There will be no application process
OL,18,Fas we will automatically identify
OL,19,Feligible individuals through existing
OL,20,Frecords."
